(41465, 118740, 4357, 2, 'From Yes I Do to No We Don''t', '如果你已離婚 你聽了會很想起舞\r\n如果你還沒離婚 你聽了會很知足\r\n如果你還沒結婚 你聽了會變成熟\r\n\r\n來自大國Gordon Tseng的英文四行詩集 GOD BLESS NOT ONLY AMERICA\r\n兩首詩：\r\nYes, I Do\r\nNo, We Don’t\r\n*\r\nYes, I Do\r\n  \r\n\r\nHis words need a love boat to ferry.\r\n\r\nHer face looks rosy, oh, very, very.\r\n\r\nTheir tale has so many promises to carry\r\n\r\nFor the right one they are ready to marry. \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nNo, We Don’t\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\nHis words become so airy.\r\n\r\nHer face looks very scary.\r\n\r\nTheir tale is nothing fairy\r\n\r\nAnd ready for an agreement to bury.\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n \r\n（中文版）\r\n\r\n從紅色證書到白色協議\r\n\r\n\r\n他的話要靠愛之船來傳達\r\n她的臉像玫瑰在陽光下\r\n故事充滿海誓山盟的對話\r\n就讓一張紅色證書來實現吧\r\n\r\n(Yes, I do!)\r\n\r\n（而王子和公主從此便過著幸福快樂的日子嗎？）\r\n\r\n他的話可別讓麥克風來放大\r\n她的臉看起來很可怕\r\n故事已經不再童話\r\n就讓一紙白色協議給埋了吧\r\n\r\n(No, we don’t!)\r\n\r\n（而王子和公主從此還會再期待幸福快樂的日子嗎？）\r\n \r\n\r\n後記：\r\n\r\n怪了，Bob Tone在Gordon Tseng的英文詩集中的一百多首詩中，一下就看上了這兩首，於是便作出了From Yes, I Do to No, We Don’t　這首搖滾歌曲（中文版：從紅色證書到白色協議）。\r\n\r\n \r\n聽聽看吧！\r\n', '2012-05-11 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 14, 'From Yes I Do to No We Don''t\r\n詞　演唱　 大國Gordon Tseng       作曲編曲　Bob Tone\r\n*\r\nHis words need a love boat to ferry.\r\nHer face looks rosy, oh, very, very.\r\nTheir tale has so many promises to carry\r\nFor the right one they are ready to marry.  \r\n\r\n（So, do they live happily hereafter?）\r\n\r\nHis words become so airy.\r\nHer face looks very scary.\r\nTheir tale is nothing fairy\r\nAnd ready for an agreement to bury.\r\n\r\n(Yes, I do!)\r\n(No, we don’t!)\r\n\r\n（So, will they expect happiness again?）\r\n\r\n\r\n（來自大國Gordon Tseng的英文四行詩集）\r\n-　from GOD BLESS NOT ONLY AMERICA\r\n', '', 300, '', 'Bob Tone', '大國Gordon Tseng', '四行倉庫', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2011-12-23 22:40:49', '2013-10-07 17:19:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
